pageContext.claim: “You look at what Hillary Clinton did with 33,000 emails and hundreds of thousands of text messages or emails going through the Weiner server or computer. Hundreds of thousands, of which many were classified. And nothing happens to her.”
pageContext.analysis: The 33,000 emails Trump is talking about from Clinton were classified retroactively. Clinton was investigated by the FBI for this episode, just as Trump was for his campaign's contacts with Russians in 2016 and for obstruction of justice.
